data.description: Located in the desirable Wimbledon subdivision, this home for sale offers the perfect combination of city convenience and established neighborhood charm. Situated just a short drive away from both Nashville and Fort Campbell, this home provides easy access to all the amenities and attractions these bustling cities have to offer. Not only does this home provide a prime location, but it also boasts a large lot that is perfect for outdoor activities and entertaining guests. Home needs some improvements and is priced accordingly. Repairs can be done prior to closing if included in contract and price adjusted accordingly.  Septic is approved for a 3 bedroom, home has 5 rooms that can be used as offices, media rooms, or bedrooms.
